1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,980
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 6 =

20
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:27,340
Officer Ren.

21
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:29,540
Is Her Majesty in the hall?

22
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:31,580
His Majesty is talking with her.

23
00:02:32,220 --> 00:02:32,980
Consort Chen deceased.

24
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:34,340
How’s her funeral arranged?

25
00:02:35,460 --> 00:02:36,940
She’s just a concubine of the late Emperor,

26
00:02:36,940 --> 00:02:38,660
why do you ask?

27
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,860
A concubine of the late Emperor?

28
00:02:44,060 --> 00:02:45,900
She is a concubine of the late Emperor now,

29
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,820
but after dozens of years,

30
00:02:48,780 --> 00:02:49,820
Are you sure

31
00:02:49,940 --> 00:02:51,860
she’s just a concubine of the late Emperor?

32
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:56,020
Her Majesty said it is ominous to

33
00:02:56,620 --> 00:02:58,780
have Consort Chen’s coffin coming out
from the West Glorious Gate,

34
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:00,380
which will bring disasters.

35
00:03:04,340 --> 00:03:05,700
It is allowed to break the wall and going through.

36
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:07,820
Breaking the wall?

37
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:10,020
That is disgraceful!

38
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:12,260
How can we treat her funeral so hastily?

39
00:03:16,180 --> 00:03:17,540
Mr. Lv, it is not reported,

40
00:03:17,540 --> 00:03:18,820
and His Majesty is still in the hall…

41
00:03:18,980 --> 00:03:19,780
No need.

42
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:21,140
If we wait any longer

43
00:03:21,420 --> 00:03:23,620
and they do break the wall
to carry Consort Chen out,

44
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:25,860
we’ll be thrown in the wild and eaten by wolves

45
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:27,660
with the descendants of Family of Liu

46
00:03:28,100 --> 00:03:30,740
after years!

47
00:03:36,260 --> 00:03:37,900
The announcement of giving her
the title of Consort Chen

48
00:03:38,180 --> 00:03:39,060
arrived at around 10 p.m. yesterday.

49
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:40,540
After less than 4 hours,

50
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:41,820
Li deceased.

51
00:03:44,460 --> 00:03:46,500
Prime Minister

52
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:48,300
Lv Yijian is waiting outside

53
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,460
to see Her Majesty.

54
00:03:51,580 --> 00:03:52,500
Let him in.

55
00:04:00,660 --> 00:04:03,540
Her Majesty,

56
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:05,180
His Majesty.

57
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:14,980
You’ve been staying with me

58
00:04:15,140 --> 00:04:16,660
for more than an hour,

59
00:04:17,460 --> 00:04:18,900
I’ve had my pulse checked and medicine taken.

60
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:22,420
I don’t want to keep you any longer.

61
00:04:34,180 --> 00:04:35,700
Have a good rest.

62
00:04:36,300 --> 00:04:40,100
I’ll go to the Hall of Politics to attend lectures.

63
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:04,860
Your Majesty.

64
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,860
You wrote three documents

65
00:05:08,820 --> 00:05:10,820
in one day asking to see me.

66
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:14,500
Is there anything urgent?

67
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:18,620
I’ve heard there’s a concubine died,

68
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:22,380
and Her Majesty announced to break
the wall of the Palace.

69
00:05:35,460 --> 00:05:37,740
Now the Prime Minister is interfering
with the harem?

70
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:41,860
Are you really

71
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:45,300
not going to think about

72
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,380
the future of Family of Liu?

73
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,060
Let go of me!

74
00:06:01,260 --> 00:06:03,100
I won’t go! Let go of me!

75
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:04,180
Let me go!

76
00:06:11,500 --> 00:06:16,180
= Li Zhi =

77
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:26,740
You are my husband.

78
00:06:28,020 --> 00:06:29,980
I’m not, I’m not.

79
00:06:31,060 --> 00:06:32,100
I don’t need a woman,

80
00:06:32,660 --> 00:06:33,780
nor a marriage.

81
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:44,740
You don’t want me to be your wife?

82
00:06:46,300 --> 00:06:48,780
No, no.

83
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:30,540
Don’t be afraid.

84
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:32,260
I’m not a witch

85
00:07:32,620 --> 00:07:34,380
I won’t take away your soul

86
00:07:34,380 --> 00:07:35,660
to prevent you from being immortal.

87
00:07:55,580 --> 00:07:56,820
As long as you write the divorce letter

88
00:07:56,820 --> 00:07:57,940
and both of us sign it,

89
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:00,580
I’ll bring the letter

90
00:08:00,700 --> 00:08:01,780
to your parents and kowtow,

91
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:03,060
and I’ll leave your home.

92
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:23,340
= Filial Piety of the Emperor =

93
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:34,700
= Keep Learning in Your Heart =

94
00:08:35,460 --> 00:08:37,300
I couldn’t see her when she’s alive,

95
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:41,100
I couldn’t look after her when she’s sick,

96
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:44,780
and now she’s dead, her funeral
can’t even be a decent one.

97
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:48,620
And there’s nothing I can do?

98
00:08:49,140 --> 00:08:50,940
There’s nothing I can do?

99
00:08:53,060 --> 00:08:54,540
She made contributions to the country,

100
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:57,980
and the servants of the country will

101
00:08:58,260 --> 00:08:59,660
fight for what she deserves.

102
00:09:03,180 --> 00:09:04,340
Servants of the country?

103
00:09:07,540 --> 00:09:09,380
Prime Minister is still waiting outside.

104
00:09:09,940 --> 00:09:13,020
It’s been a couple of hours.

105
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:14,860
Let him wait.

106
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,140
I can’t believe

107
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:22,100
the funeral

108
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:25,180
of a concubine

109
00:09:25,460 --> 00:09:27,220
can turn my son against me!

110
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:30,420
I’ve raised him for more than twenty years,

111
00:09:31,340 --> 00:09:32,420
I’ve taken good care of him

112
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:33,860
in every detail.

113
00:09:35,660 --> 00:09:36,740
I’d like to see

114
00:09:38,620 --> 00:09:39,820
if he’s going to

115
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,420
ruin my family in the future

116
00:09:41,460 --> 00:09:42,900
for a concubine

117
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:44,860
he barely saw.

118
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:47,540
Your Majesty,

119
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,380
if the deceased

120
00:09:50,380 --> 00:09:52,020
is only a normal concubine,

121
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:55,180
why did you give her the title of Consort Chen

122
00:09:55,180 --> 00:09:57,420
when she was severely sick?

123
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:01,940
People all know

124
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:03,420
you and His Majesty have a good relationship.

125
00:10:04,260 --> 00:10:05,660
You’ve done nothing wrong

126
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,140
to the court, to the late Emperor

127
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:08,820
and His Majesty.

128
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:11,820
His Majesty has been obedient to you

129
00:10:11,820 --> 00:10:12,980
as a flawless son.

130
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:16,820
Only with your wisdom

131
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:18,020
and his benevolence

132
00:10:18,020 --> 00:10:20,260
can we have the peace of the country.

133
00:10:22,460 --> 00:10:23,260
Your Majesty,

134
00:10:24,340 --> 00:10:25,700
why do you

135
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:27,180
ruin your relationship

136
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:30,420
for a deceased concubine?

137
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:42,660
You just said

138
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:46,380
you’ve raised him

139
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:49,060
for more than twenty years,

140
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:50,940
do you think you are not as important as

141
00:10:52,220 --> 00:10:53,420
a concubine

142
00:10:53,580 --> 00:10:55,620
who he barely saw?

143
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:58,100
Your Majesty,

144
00:10:59,180 --> 00:11:01,300
the feelings His Majesty has for Li

145
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:04,060
is nothing more than guilt.

146
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,580
Are you really going to

147
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:10,140
turn his guilt

148
00:11:10,740 --> 00:11:12,620
into hatred

149
00:11:12,620 --> 00:11:14,180
on such an impulse?

150
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:26,580
= Ms. Sheng =

151
00:11:34,820 --> 00:11:35,660
Ms. Sheng,

152
00:11:36,260 --> 00:11:38,100
we’re travelling in a hurry.

153
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:39,300
The linchpin is wore down

154
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:40,260
and broke.

155
00:11:40,780 --> 00:11:42,140
We still need to go for an hour,

156
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:44,540
I’ll fix the linchpin before we continue.

157
00:11:44,980 --> 00:11:46,220
Have a rest.

158
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:47,940
Drink some tea.

159
00:11:57,620 --> 00:11:58,460
Sir,

160
00:12:01,460 --> 00:12:02,500
can you help me

161
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:03,780
and take me to the Capital?

162
00:12:09,020 --> 00:12:10,540
Are you going to the direction of the Palace?

163
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:15,700
Yes.

164
00:12:17,180 --> 00:12:18,460
My family lives nearby the Palace.

165
00:12:18,940 --> 00:12:20,260
Can you give me a ride?

166
00:12:29,780 --> 00:12:30,740
I don’t have money with me,

167
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:33,220
but this hairpin is made of pure gold.

168
00:12:33,660 --> 00:12:34,700
Please take it.

169
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:42,700
Come.

170
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:03,260
Thank you.

171
00:13:19,820 --> 00:13:20,500
Your Majesty,

172
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:22,940
an hour ago,

173
00:13:23,500 --> 00:13:25,060
Prime Minister Lv left the Hall of
Benevolence and Longevity.

174
00:13:25,740 --> 00:13:28,140
Later, Ren Shouzhong announced Her Majesty’s words.

175
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:32,340
Consort Chen was honest and tolerant.

176
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:33,940
She gave birth to princess,

177
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:36,260
and stayed in the royal mausoleum for decades.

178
00:13:37,140 --> 00:13:38,180
Now she deserves

179
00:13:38,900 --> 00:13:39,780
a decent funeral.

180
00:13:40,980 --> 00:13:42,540
She’ll be honored in Jiaqing Yard.

181
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:45,420
The court will be closed for three days
starting from tomorrow.

182
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:49,580
Three days later, her coffin will be sent to

183
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,420
and buried in the Yard of Luck.

184
00:13:53,220 --> 00:13:54,100
Titles will be given to three
generations of her descendants.

185
00:14:22,460 --> 00:14:23,980
I took fifty thousand,

186
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:25,500
some silk and utensils

187
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:27,180
to award to people who served madam.

188
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:29,860
Her Majesty also gave some awards.

189
00:14:30,380 --> 00:14:32,300
None of them wanted to stay in the Palace,

190
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:34,140
so I sent

191
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:35,300
them home.

192
00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:39,540
She had been sick for a while,

193
00:14:40,980 --> 00:14:42,860
but this attack was unexpected,

194
00:14:43,420 --> 00:14:44,980
and they got panicked.

195
00:14:45,780 --> 00:14:46,900
Maybe they didn’t notice

196
00:14:47,100 --> 00:14:48,300
or hear

197
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:49,460
what she said

198
00:14:49,460 --> 00:14:50,660
or mentioned.

199
00:14:57,620 --> 00:14:58,900
I insisted to ask you

200
00:14:58,900 --> 00:15:00,500
to bring them to the Palace,

201
00:15:01,900 --> 00:15:03,580
wondering if she had anything

202
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:04,420
to say to me.

203
00:15:06,620 --> 00:15:07,700
What a fool I was.

204
00:15:09,580 --> 00:15:10,380
I think

205
00:15:12,060 --> 00:15:13,380
she never saw herself

206
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,620
as my mother.

207
00:15:16,460 --> 00:15:18,300
Her worries and care about me

208
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:20,220
are just

209
00:15:21,100 --> 00:15:22,740
greed and improper thought to her

210
00:15:24,180 --> 00:15:25,660
that needed to be removed from her mind.

211
00:15:28,900 --> 00:15:31,300
How can she mention me to others?

212
00:15:33,580 --> 00:15:34,620
If she forgot

213
00:15:34,620 --> 00:15:36,180
my existence,

214
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:38,860
it might be a good thing.

215
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:43,140
Wish she can

216
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:46,900
reunite with my sister in peace.

217
00:16:08,540 --> 00:16:09,900
I’ve read the proposal from the Ministry of Rites

218
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:13,100
about the visit to the ancestral temple
in February.

219
00:16:15,700 --> 00:16:16,740
I only changed the part

220
00:16:16,740 --> 00:16:18,140
about my dress.

221
00:16:19,500 --> 00:16:20,380
And other parts

222
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,700
remain the same.

223
00:16:38,380 --> 00:16:41,500
I’ve read the proposal

224
00:16:41,780 --> 00:16:43,420
reviewed by Her Majesty

225
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:47,140
carefully yesterday.

226
00:16:48,140 --> 00:16:49,260
You are still confused

227
00:16:49,660 --> 00:16:51,860
about the dress.

228
00:16:52,580 --> 00:16:55,780
So I read Rites of the Zhou again,

229
00:16:56,020 --> 00:16:59,740
and copied the part about the empress dress

230
00:17:00,100 --> 00:17:01,340
to discuss it at the court.

231
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:13,460
The six dresses of the empress are,

232
00:17:14,100 --> 00:17:17,300
Weiyi, Yudi, Quedi,

233
00:17:17,700 --> 00:17:22,100
Juyi, Zhanyi, Yuanyi and Susha.

234
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:46,620
Executive Yan,

235
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:49,100
are you muddled in your head

236
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:51,500
or you can’t understand what I wrote?

237
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:53,980
I am not confused.

238
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:55,900
I am sober.

239
00:17:57,220 --> 00:17:59,620
I wrote that in February

240
00:18:00,540 --> 00:18:03,020
I’ll wear dragon robe to visit
the ancestral temple.

241
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,020
I think

242
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:18,380
it is against the conventions.

243
00:18:18,460 --> 00:18:20,100
You shouldn’t do it.

244
00:18:28,100 --> 00:18:30,140
I’ve been managing the court for ten years.

245
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:33,460
Every day I review your proposals

246
00:18:33,660 --> 00:18:35,140
and attend to state affairs.

247
00:18:38,220 --> 00:18:39,860
Why can’t I wear dragon robe

248
00:18:41,620 --> 00:18:43,260
to visit the ancestral temple?

249
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:55,700
= Xue Kui, courtesy name Suyi =
With all my respect,

250
00:18:56,540 --> 00:19:00,100
how are you going to face the ancestors

251
00:19:01,700 --> 00:19:04,780
and the late Emperor

252
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:09,260
in the dragon robe for the Son of Heaven?

253
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:23,860
Stand up, Mr. Xue.

254
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:30,140
The procedure of visiting the ancestral temple

255
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:32,940
changes every year.

256
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:36,980
Officials in charge always argue about it,

257
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,580
quoting classics and history.

258
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:42,620
Her Majesty feels unwell today,

259
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:44,260
and needs to go back to take a rest.

260
00:19:46,220 --> 00:19:47,020
So much for today.

261
00:19:48,140 --> 00:19:49,380
The procedure of temple visiting

262
00:19:49,860 --> 00:19:51,380
shall be discussed by relevant ministries.

263
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:03,980
= Following Strict Laws and Disciplines =

264
00:20:07,460 --> 00:20:08,220
Your Majesty,

265
00:20:09,020 --> 00:20:09,940
I’ve copied

266
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:11,540
Physicians diagnosis

267
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:12,820
of Her Majesty.

268
00:20:19,580 --> 00:20:20,500
Recently,

269
00:20:21,180 --> 00:20:23,020
she’s becoming worse and worse.

270
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:24,740
She can’t even lie down on the bed.

271
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:26,940
Physicians have used

272
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:28,100
the strongest medicine,

273
00:20:28,220 --> 00:20:29,460
but she’s not getting any better.

274
00:20:36,060 --> 00:20:36,860
Maoze,

275
00:20:37,780 --> 00:20:39,740
let’s go to Mr. Yan’s residence.

276
00:20:39,900 --> 00:20:40,620
Yes.

277
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:51,500
♪ Chinese parasols were rustled by the swift wind ♪

278
00:20:53,100 --> 00:21:02,140
♪ In bleak and hazy moonlight ♪

279
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:10,100
♪ I was constantly awakened from sweat dream ♪

280
00:21:10,100 --> 00:21:18,740
♪ By the scream of geese from afar ♪

281
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:22,460
♪ From afar ♪

282
00:21:24,900 --> 00:21:27,540
Listen to the music by the lake,
