you didn’t perform those years.

565
00:35:25,180 --> 00:35:27,020
All the tolerance you had

566
00:35:28,820 --> 00:35:30,740
is for that day.

567
00:35:34,580 --> 00:35:36,260
But that day never came.

568
00:35:38,260 --> 00:35:39,820
So you hate me,

569
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:41,700
right?

570
00:35:47,900 --> 00:35:49,620
I want you to recover.

571
00:35:53,260 --> 00:35:55,020
You prayed for me,

572
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:58,860
announced amnesty for me,

573
00:36:01,540 --> 00:36:02,820
but you put the people

574
00:36:02,820 --> 00:36:04,180
who wanted to take me down

575
00:36:04,180 --> 00:36:05,700
and who stood against me

576
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:07,420
back to their positions.

577
00:36:08,300 --> 00:36:09,740
Kou Zhun, Cao Liyong,

578
00:36:09,740 --> 00:36:10,940
Zhou Huaizheng, Zhou Wenzhi,

579
00:36:10,940 --> 00:36:12,300
are these their names?

580
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:13,780
Am I correct?

581
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:15,540
By doing so,

582
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:18,900
you are telling the country

583
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:23,180
that the court is in your hand,

584
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:24,900
and the country

585
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:28,180
is the Zhao’s,

586
00:36:28,700 --> 00:36:29,940
right?

587
00:36:40,100 --> 00:36:41,180
The country

588
00:36:43,460 --> 00:36:45,300
is originally the Zhao’s.

589
00:36:47,820 --> 00:36:48,820
You’ve managed the country for the late Emperor

590
00:36:48,820 --> 00:36:49,980
for so many years,

591
00:36:51,180 --> 00:36:52,780
and now you should feel glad

592
00:36:54,180 --> 00:36:55,500
to give it back to me,

593
00:36:56,500 --> 00:36:57,260
right?

594
00:37:01,980 --> 00:37:03,540
People like Kou Zhun and Cao Liyong

595
00:37:04,660 --> 00:37:06,180
are capable officials.

596
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:11,300
They are loyal to the late Emperor and the country.

597
00:37:13,380 --> 00:37:14,740
They fought against you

598
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:16,180
because of suspicion

599
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:18,500
or narrow mind.

600
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:21,380
But they are not completely evil.

601
00:37:23,220 --> 00:37:24,340
If remitting

602
00:37:24,340 --> 00:37:25,460
their crimes

603
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:27,860
can bring you good luck

604
00:37:28,420 --> 00:37:29,500
and health,

605
00:37:31,980 --> 00:37:33,740
and write off the past,

606
00:37:35,220 --> 00:37:37,260
it’s a huge blessing to our country.

607
00:37:38,140 --> 00:37:38,860
Isn’t this

608
00:37:40,060 --> 00:37:41,140
a good thing?

609
00:37:47,980 --> 00:37:49,820
You really pray for me?

610
00:37:53,180 --> 00:37:54,420
I want you to recover.

611
00:37:58,020 --> 00:37:59,300
Few days later

612
00:38:00,340 --> 00:38:02,060
we’ll visit the ancestral temple.

613
00:38:03,580 --> 00:38:05,060
If you want to wear the dragon robe

614
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:06,020
to worship the ancestors,

615
00:38:07,980 --> 00:38:08,860
then do it.

616
00:38:38,740 --> 00:38:39,280
= Xinchou =

617
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:42,280
= It is allowed to for the Empress Dowager
to wear the dragon robe =

618
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:44,280
= without the pattern of alga and vessel
and two tassels, and without wearing swords. =

619
00:38:44,280 --> 00:38:46,280
= The robe has sixteen dragon flowers =

620
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:48,280
= and 12 tassels both in the front and back.=

621
00:38:48,280 --> 00:38:50,300
= The dress she wears to worship
is under the name of dragon gown. =

622
00:39:19,980 --> 00:39:20,700
= The second year of Mingdao =
Your Majesty,

623
00:39:21,420 --> 00:39:22,460
Your Majesty.

624
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:24,100
What do you want to say?

625
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:26,820
If you can’t say it,

626
00:39:27,220 --> 00:39:28,580
write it in my palm.

627
00:39:29,020 --> 00:39:29,820
No matter what you ask,

628
00:39:29,820 --> 00:39:30,660
I’ll do it for you.

629
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:36,060
Mr. Zhao.

630
00:39:49,260 --> 00:39:50,060
Your Majesty,

631
00:40:07,580 --> 00:40:08,780
I’ve tried acupuncture

632
00:40:09,100 --> 00:40:11,460
but Her Majesty still can’t talk.

633
00:40:11,700 --> 00:40:12,940
She just keeps

634
00:40:13,140 --> 00:40:15,220
tearing apart her dress.

635
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:20,260
Her Majesty doesn’t want to meet the late Emperor

636
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:21,420
in the dress of emperor.

637
00:40:23,660 --> 00:40:26,220
I beg you, Your Majesty,

638
00:40:27,020 --> 00:40:29,860
change her dress to Empress dress.

639
00:40:37,180 --> 00:40:38,460
Take Empress dress

640
00:40:40,020 --> 00:40:41,660
and change for her.

641
00:41:59,780 --> 00:42:01,220
What do you think, Your Majesty?

642
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:08,700
Do you think

643
00:42:11,500 --> 00:42:12,660
if it’s appropriate?

644
00:42:36,620 --> 00:42:46,300
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

645
00:42:47,620 --> 00:42:55,980
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

646
00:42:58,820 --> 00:43:03,540
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

647
00:43:04,500 --> 00:43:08,660
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

648
00:43:10,100 --> 00:43:15,580
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

649
00:43:15,580 --> 00:43:20,380
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

650
00:43:24,060 --> 00:43:29,700
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

651
00:43:29,700 --> 00:43:34,580
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

652
00:43:35,100 --> 00:43:40,860
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

653
00:43:40,860 --> 00:43:45,940
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

654
00:43:46,380 --> 00:43:51,300
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

655
00:43:51,940 --> 00:43:56,780
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

656
00:43:57,460 --> 00:44:02,620
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

657
00:44:03,100 --> 00:44:08,140
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

658
00:44:08,700 --> 00:44:12,780
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

659
00:44:14,220 --> 00:44:18,860
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

660
00:44:19,900 --> 00:44:25,060
♪ The howling wind ♪

661
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:29,500
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

662
00:44:30,980 --> 00:44:35,900
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

663
00:44:36,540 --> 00:44:41,780
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

664
00:44:42,180 --> 00:44:47,460
♪ The howling wind ♪

665
00:44:47,780 --> 00:44:52,660
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

666
00:44:53,260 --> 00:44:59,980
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
